                    "value": "<p>When not discorporated, a flotsam terror has an outer shell of seaweed and nautical debris. This shell has Hardness from the amalgamation of objects. Once a flotsam terror is reduced to fewer than half its Hit Points, its wreckage armor breaks, removing the Hardness and reducing its Armor Class to 17.</p>"
